<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pile-n">pile <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /paɪl/    美 /paɪl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>堆；摞：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a pile of books 
一摞书</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>大量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Most of the students’time was spent at school doing <strong>piles of</strong> homework. 
学生的大部分时间都用来在学校做大量的作业。</p><footer>2008 湖北改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We received <strong>piles of</strong> letters from readers. 
我们收到了大量的读者来信。</p></div></div>